cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SD

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and semantic space construction.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper introduces a new neural network architecture for constructing the common semantic space.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with knowledge and resource transfer across languages.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper mentions extrinsic evaluation using low-resource language name tagging.
- cs.SD (Sound) is the least likely category as the paper does not deal with any audio or sound-related tasks.
